headline: Fal.Con Event Boosts CrowdStrike (CRWD) as Investors Cheer AI Strategy
summary: CrowdStrike Holdings, Inc. (NASDAQ:CRWD) is one of the AI Stocks Every Investor Should Watch. On September 24, Bernstein SocGen Group analyst Peter Weed reiterated a Market Perform rating on the stock with a $343.00 price target. headline: What Recent Price Swings Mean for CrowdStrike’s Valuation in 2025
summary: If you own or are eyeing shares of CrowdStrike Holdings, you are in good company. The stock has been impossible to ignore, racking up an impressive 38.6% gain so far this year and soaring 68.4% over the last twelve months. In fact, looking further back, its return over the past five years stands at an eye-opening 244.2%. Granted, it is not all smooth sailing.
